Name: Nightmare Gabriel
StarDesc: ['Clear Stage', 'Have less than 2 characters rebooted', 'Have no characters rebooted']

Name: Wispthorn
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\nNo one knew what Luna was thinking when she made herself this Coating. The glowing thorns entangled her like everlasting shackles. ""May the apostates burn in the fire of these thorns."""

Name: Florescence
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\nShe quietly awaits, like a blooming bud that awaits to be picked up, hoping that her feelings would one day be discovered."

Name: Grace
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\nShe had witnessed many lives stepping into the divine hall. Never had she thought that one day that she could wear this outfit herself, as you took her hand in the blessed light."

Name: Scarlet Spring
SingleDescription:
"No Stamina cost

When spring returns to the garden, flowers would blossom brilliantly.
The elegant pattern is made from a traditional gold-weaving technique.
Qu does not have many opportunities to wear this outfit, but she still hopes this indispensable part of Tabula Akasha can be shown to the world."

Name: Azure Apocalypse
SingleDescription:
"No Stamina cost

Finally, it is over, and all the noises in the world come to a screeching halt.
She returns to you, freed from all the thorns brought by the fate.
You have each other for all the time from now on."

Name: Howling Crown
SingleDescription:
"No Stamina cost

When all things are silent, she still holds the shining spear up high.
For she vows to protect, save, and uphold this world with dignity.
You are the first to discover her in the snow."

Name: Honor Model
SingleDescription: "No Stamina Cost\n\nThe custom-made uniform of the outstanding graduates of F.O.S. It is close-fitting but does not impede movement, flashy but not ostentatious, suitable for attending various occasions. The pure gold chain presiding on the chest always reminds the dresser to shoulder the mission of the elite, to hang the honor and responsibility on the heart, and to become a glorious example to lead the crowd."

Name: Street Rebellion
SingleDescription: "No Stamina Cost\n\nWith young and frivolous as the main concept of the design, the coating shows the rebellion and self of the lone wolf girl. Just standing at the corner of the street in this dress, it seems that it can release an aura that strangers are not allowed to approach."

Name: Nosferatu
SingleDescription: "No Stamina Cost\n\nHe drinks up a glass of redness in the dark night in the song of praise sung by all beings. Although unable to embrace the light, he would still guard you silently in the darkness."

Name: Deed of Snow Leopard
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\n""What can I do for you, Commandant...? Wait! Why do I have to do this?"" Although there is anger in the girl's eyes, she will only bare her fangs when she tries to protect her allies. She will also try her best to temporarily disguise herself for missions. And of course, she won't let anyone take her most important customer away from her."

Name: Spring Huntress
SingleDescription: "No Stamina Cost\n\nInspired by a royal spring hunting tradition thousands of years ago, this coating combines the traditional archer costume with the aristocratic clothing style. It dispels misfortune and misery that imprison the world with the sound of the deities and brings back spring."

Name: Tiger Imperium
SingleDescription: "No Stamina Cost\n\nA tiger general charges onto the battlefield, slashing at the enemies with his greatsword. To fit the user's untamed style, this new coating is designed with various wild animal patterns that seem to carry the power of a mythical oriental beast, making the user look even fiercer."

Name: Illusionist
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost.\n\nThe magician hides the special gift he prepared in advance with magic and pulls out a red heart with a brilliant magic skill. Even though the audience is already impressed, the magician's eyes are only fixed on only one of them. Now, he has put the response in your hand."

Name: Dreamweaver
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost.\n\nA Coating made based on Pulao's description of her dream. With great passion, Pulao described the tea room waiters, the old man who sold prune drinks, and the shop owner who recommended her this suit. ""Char siu buns are the best!"" ""You look like an idol in this suit!"" These sentences always echo in everyone's M.I.N.D. after Pulao's passionate interpretation."

Name: Wavebender
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\nShe has reduced her armor to the minimum to make sure that she can surf freely in the feast of music. However, what interests her more is to lie under a sunshade and watch how helpless you are until she calls you when the time's right, ""Commandant, get that for me."" As a reward, she will share the small space under her sunshade with you."

Name: Exorcist
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\nThe exorcist's lamp shines bright before her chest with her silver blade reflecting her beautiful face. With her golden eyes fixed on the shadow of the past, she will eventually find out the truth at the end of the dark realm."

Name: Niki US1000
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost.\n\n""Power system online, wind-pressure balance calibrated, GPS configuration completed... Would you guide me to claim victory in battle once again?"""

Name: Radiant Respite
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\nEven though he was not the initiator, he managed to give you a trip that was perfect for you. With the stars coming out above, he smiles under a street lamp, waving his hand. A night breeze gently puts a period on this date of yours, but before saying your goodbyes, you lightly readjust his slipping scarf. He would never have thought such a trivial move is already enough to make an ever-cool-headed person like him skip a heartbeat."

Name: Fiery Moon
SingleDescription: "The fantasy of the pale moon has sealed the false god's grace, for it scorns lives fallen into corruption. She needs no daylight for her glory. With a mere gesture of hers, the ruins of a shattered sanctum will rise anew. Travelers back to the world, have you captured the light fleeting in her eyes?"

Name: Vox Solaris
SingleDescription:
"She gazes at the morning dew at dawn and starry sky at night. When spring arrives, she wanders along the melting river; when autumn comes, she touches the fallen petals.
On rainy days, the girl plays her music alone in the secluded temple, waiting for the sun to rise again.
Accompanied by the sky and four seasons, she grasps the remaining fragments.
No matter how far they are apart from each other and if the world responds to her invocation, she will keep praying for the one she misses.
The rain gradually eases off in the sound of her flute. When dawn comes, the bell rings too.
When the sky clears, flowers will bloom again."

Name: Zhuolu's Rain
SingleDescription: Lightning rips the day; dark stars fall at night.\nFriendship, sacrifices, betrayals—she's ditched a lot but carries memories etched in her skin, a tapestry of ancient battles. It's her proof "they" were real.\nAs history turns to legends and myths get passed down, what kind of world now reflects in the eyes of this lone wanderer?

Name: March Hare
SingleDescription: "Out with the old, in with the new—the rabbit brings spring back."

Name: 冥夜の日冠
SingleDescription: "She is a radiant sun that unfurls the banner to illuminate the darkness. She is the winds of the underworld that howl across the sky to mark the border between life and death. She is the vanguard of the gods, the leader of heroic souls, the deity silently awaiting the long night. When the sun sets and the sacred ibis spreads its wings, will you join her in an eternal expedition to defend the oath sworn by both of you?"

Name: Vermillion Bargain
SingleDescription: "She turns her back against the gods in the deepest night and chants the forbidden spell with her life. Flickering candlelight sways over her familiar face. No matter how long you have parted from each other, the pact and oath you made will eventually light up the lost memories, bringing back everything that was once lost. ""...I have come to fulfill the Crimson Pact."""

Name: Azure Apocalypse
SingleDescription:
"No Stamina cost

Finally, it is over, and all the noises in the world come to a screeching halt.
She returns to you, freed from all the thorns brought by the fate.
You have each other for all the time from now on."

Name: Nocturnal Watch
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\n\nThe light of the day never knows how dark the night is.

Name: Abyssal Dye
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\nWhispered to be a siren by some and a guardian goddess by others, her tears hold the promise of miraculous healing and eternal life. Countless travelers have embarked on quests in search of these tears... However, what moves her heart to shed those drops?"

Name: Nightbreaker
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\nThe starlight in her hand pierces through the darkness to open a new dawn from the white glow. She reveals her new blade as she walks on the edge of freedom, her silhouette, her steps, and her flames reforged by the blazing star."

Name: Dazzler
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\n""The keynote of the battlefield is not black, white, or gray!"" Every leap of the girl will be the strongest order in the battle game."

Name: Ashen Wings
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\nFalling into a boundless dark dream, she changes into a gown weaved from gray feathers and embraces splendid illusions in the misty world. Before the wonderland fades away, she hums the song of yesterday."

Name: Revival Remedy
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\n""Wearing a white gown, she taps the sign next to her. There are three words written on it: 'Hands of Miracle'. Turns out she is the renowned 'Reincarnation of the Legendary Doctor'..."" —Excerpted from Tales of the Babylonia Legends"

Name: Moonlight Soliloquy
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\nThe silver moon weaves a night sky lit by star dust. The girl gracefully sketches a white world, cleansing the night's clamor."

Name: Vow of Dragon
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\n\nThe unsheathed blade slashes through the air with thunderous speed like a crimson dragon. The earth awakes to her arrival as spring returns.

Name: Pyrewatch
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\nHer sword burns down all the guilty souls, and her staff purges all the restless shadows. Her white outfit is soaked in the blood of the heretics; her fiery wings play a requiem for the sinful ones."

Name: Flying Apsara
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\nClouds as her clothes, she gently plays the pipa like an Apsara, making people want to walk into an old dream that has lasted a thousand years along with the heavenly melody."

Name: Twilight Veil
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\nThe girl whispers prayers under the stars in the twilight. She nocks the arrow and draws the white bow of the stars to chase away the mist, clearing the thorns for the lost ones along with the martyrs' souls behind her."

Name: Tiny Bad Wolf
SingleDescription: "No Stamina required\n\nIn a honey-like dream, the explorer follows the balloon into a funfair. Passing by floats and hot air balloons with her agile strides, she stops at the Ferris wheel and decides to place sea salt ice cream second on her hunting list."

Name: Blue Crush
SingleDescription: "No Stamina required\n\nHolding her paintbrush, she adds a rainbow of vibrant colors to the golden coastline she has painted. Under the embrace of the summer sun, with the sound of a soda can popping open, she records yet another summer on her canvas."

Name: Prestigious Accolade
SingleDescription: "No Stamina Cost\n\nIf darkness becomes an endless, unyielding dream—what then? Let a raven's shriek rend the heavens to forge her hymn of triumph. When infernos claw at the gray veil of skies, when flames devour the cursed soil to smoldering silence, she rises, armored in dawn's first light, ablaze with glory's unforgiving radiance."

Name: Warding Ritualist
SingleDescription:
"Does not consume Stamina.

On the Ghost Festival, the Earth Deity grants absolution.
A young woman in a flowing Taoist robe walks along the ancient path, a cool night breeze ruffling her hair. Tonight, the gates of the underworld swing open. Spirits, nourished by the offerings of their descendants, wander aimlessly, searching for sustenance. The young woman shakes her bell, lays out food and drink, and offers blessings to guide the lost souls to peaceful rest. But some resentful spirits refuse to be appeased and seek to wreak havoc on the mortal world. Whenever she encounters one, she lets out a scornful laugh, swings her hammer with furious force, and roars,
""Ingrates! I'll send you straight to oblivion!"""

Name: Candy Rider
SingleDescription: "Does not consume Stamina.\n\nAs twilight fades and the city bids farewell to the day, countless neon lights awaken. Under their glow, a girl quietly steps onto the ice rink. Unwrapping a piece of candy, she sets off with the whirring of her skates, leaving the noise and worries of the world behind as she speeds against the flow of time."

Name: Hell Sing
SingleDescription: "Does not consume Stamina.\n\nHis figure blurs against the backdrop of the desert, and the mark on his chest, of unknown origin, is as faded as the abandoned land itself. The self-exiled wanderer draws his blade. Only villains remain in this place, and moments later, their eyes hold only fear and despair."

Name: Wings of Equilibrium
SingleDescription: "No Stamina Cost\n\nThe first glimmers of starlight appear along the sky's edge. A lady with a goddess-like aura sits atop a hill. Her expectant gaze is fixed on the restless sea. All of a sudden, a solitary sail breaks free from the tempest's grip, steering toward a distant horizon... Her lips curve into a faint smile as she twirls her quill, etching yet another hero's legend into her annals."

Name: Carmine Ripples
SingleDescription: "No Stamina Cost\n\nKnown only to a few, a legend promises that mermaids who vault an emerald cascade will rise to divinity with scales sloughing away. A maiden drifts among her kin, yet her eyes cannot help but steal glances at the rainbow bridge behind with her mind ablaze with memories of clan oaths and ancestral chains. What worth is divinity if freedom lies beyond her grasp? In a surge of resolve, she turns around, plunging herself down from the bridge, toward the world of humanity."

Name: Resplendent Debut
SingleDescription: "No Stamina cost\n\nOpera performers take turns to come up on stage in elaborate costumes with their graceful movements and expressive singing drawing all eyes under the stage to them. In this moment, years of hard work off stage have paid off. Despite the hardship, the performers' dedication to opera has never changed. They're willing to explain the splendid world to the entire audience."

Name: Obsidian Balladeer
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nThe girl journeys through the endless shift between day and night, expressing her feelings through the sonnet. She plucks the strings, and in the lost season, the shadow under the dim light no longer leads to the journey back. She hums along to announce the beginning of the next play.

Name: Tapestry of Spring
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nRing out the old year and ring in the new with a new melody and the tapestry of spring. The girl infuses her best wishes into the window paper-cuts she made and put them up in the lingering coldness of the spring and the sound of firecrackers.

Name: Fatal Temptation
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nPeople say a femme fatale can never truly win, yet she has found exactly what she longs for. The poor soul never had a chance to walk away unscathed—every fateful encounter beneath the late night, every meticulously planned ball... Sweet, shifting sands have already engulfed your sanity. The sharp heel of her stiletto presses against your red heart. The color of her lips is the perfect accent to the glint in her eyes. They say to stay away—but who could stop you from falling into this temptation?

Name: Hollow Crown
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nDevoured by the flames and reborn in the ashes, she travels alone on the edges of the shattered lands. She is the lord of the doom fire and the end of humanity made flesh.

Name: Starward Dragon
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nWhere the wild lands end, a low cry breaks the silence after the sun sets behind the mountains. A dragon comes out and spreads her wings under the stars, embarking on an infinite journey against fate to awaken the slumbering world.

Name: Ritual of Souls
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nThrough veils of mist, the divine maiden hums a song, offering tribute to the heavens. She lowers her gaze, her fingers brushing through the sands of time, awakening spirits that have long slumbered for centuries. Amidst the fleeting mist, she seeks the answer till eternity.

Name: Sandy Spectrum
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nAmidst the rhythm of waves crashing ashore, the girl leaps gracefully into the air. The pale violet silhouette flashes from behind, sending a spike through the air with precision. As the whistle blows, she and her sister exchange a smile and turn to face their opponents: "That was a warning for your foul."

Name: Thorns of Crimson
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nUnder a sky veiled in dying embers, pale remnants of the dead wander endlessly in this cursed world, where even death brings no rest. Among the ruins of the sacred sanctuary decorated by fallen idols, she lights a candle and prays with quiet devotion, bringing peace to each soul still clinging to sorrow and resolve, refusing to be swallowed by the void.

Name: Infernal Deliverance
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nPlague is the whisper of the dead, and it is my duty to silence them... forever. In the Annihilation Zone, a raven-beaked shadow roams, guiding twisted souls into eternal stillness with the blade of a scalpel. It's not salvation, he says, but the final mercy for the living.

Name: Sparragon's Triumph
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nOn the day of the Sparragon's Triumph, all legions shall kneel in surrender. She stands before the shattered flagpole, the Gibbous Edge afloat in her palm. Her shoulder plates shape into bronze birds, her blade gleaming beneath lazuline feathers. Before the throne lie the fallen; behind it rises the glory of Kowloong. Dust shall be wiped away with blood - traitors, banished for eternity.

Name: Sash of Silence
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\n\nBeneath a sky choked with dust and blotted sun, ancient sands devour the broken steles of fallen gods. As the world-drowning dust storm swallows the last sliver of twilight, she emerges from the depths of this abyss where the dead gather. The divinities of ruin bow their heads, bestowing upon the newcomer the honor known as eternal silence. She is the shepherd who comforts all lost souls, and the general who commands death itself. She walks the fractured boundaries between existence and oblivion, gazing over the hunting grounds where eternity has fallen mute. In her realm, there is nothing—only the void's quietude, soundlessly proclaiming: death is the most ancient mercy life can receive.

Name: Roulette of Stolen Time
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\n\nThe bone-white roulette wheel spins on, its madness never ceasing. None know when the game began, just as none can tally the souls mortgaged beneath the mountain of chips. To win everything, only to lose it all? Victory and defeat are but two faces of the same gilded Mammon Coin. As the golden flash of a card decides a fate, she smiles, gathering her opponents' fear and despair into her coffers. The house, after all, has no need for luck—only the patience to wait for the next soul to lay everything on the table.

Name: Lotus Ballad
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nUnder the tall window, the girl cuts and sews her own gown from soft silk, dyed in the gentle colors of mist and water, carrying the cool scent of lotus dew. In the quiet night breeze, she walks with calm steps to meet the one returning home. She lifts her hand in invitation, wishing only to stay together, to share dawn and dusk, and to watch the flowers bloom through every season.
